# OnePortal Backend Rules

## Package Structure

```
controller/   ← REST endpoints only (no business logic)
service/      ← all business logic + permission checks
repository/   ← JPA only, no custom SQL in controllers
dto/          ← nested static classes inside one outer DTO class per domain
entity/       ← @Entity, never returned from controllers
exception/    ← ResourceNotFoundException, AccessDeniedException
```

## Entity Pattern

```java
@Entity @Table(name = "...")
@Getter @Setter @NoArgsConstructor @AllArgsConstructor @Builder
public class Foo {
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY) private Long id;
    @CreatedDate @Column(updatable = false) private LocalDateTime createdAt;
    @LastModifiedDate private LocalDateTime updatedAt;
}
```

- Use `@ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)` for all associations — never `EAGER`
- Use `@Builder.Default` when initialising collections in Lombok builders
- Define enums as inner classes of the entity they belong to

## DTO Pattern — Nested Static Classes

```java
public class FooDTO {
    @Value @Builder public static class FooResponse { ... }   // immutable response
    @Data public static class CreateFooRequest { ... }        // Jackson-deserialised request
}
```

- Never expose JPA entities from controllers — always map to DTO

## Service Pattern

- Class-level `@Transactional(readOnly = true)`, override with `@Transactional` on writes
- Always verify requester role before mutating: check both `User.Role` (global) and `ProjectMember.ProjectRole` (project-level)
- Throw `ResourceNotFoundException` (triggers 404), `AccessDeniedException` (triggers 403)
- When deleting parent entity, manually delete children lacking cascade (rows → sheet → project)

## Controller Pattern

```java
@RestController @RequestMapping("/api/v1/...")
@RequiredArgsConstructor @Tag(name = "...")
```

- Use `@RequestParam Long requesterId` — no Spring Security principal yet (Phase 2)
- Use `@Operation(summary = "...")` on every endpoint
- Return DTOs, never entities

## Flyway

- New migration: `src/main/resources/db/migration/V<next>__description.sql`
- Never edit an existing migration file
